<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2018-06-30</DATELINE><TITLE>The Expanding Diversity of RNA Viruses in Vertebrates</TITLE><BODY>The diversity of RNA viruses in vertebrates remains largely unexplored. The discovery of 214 novel vertebrate-associated RNA viruses will likely help us to understand the diversity and evolution of RNA viruses in vertebrates.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>